   "en": "Rookie editor Amemiya takes over the responsibility of handling the popular mystery author Hayama Yaichi. However, he finds out that the author he admires is actually not good at cleaning up after himself and always has dark circles under his eyes. When Amemiya, worried about Hayama’s health, forces him to get some sleep, Hayama suddenly hugs him and says, “...Then, let’s stay like this for a while,” and uses him as a pillow…!? A healing love story between a gloomy author and a puppy-like junior editor!"
